<plot>Inspired by the French film The Red Balloon, The Pink Dress chronicles the travels of a very pink bridesmaid's dress. Featuring all original music, this silent film was written, directed, produced, and entirely crewed by women. "This is a story about perception. It expresses the subjective nature of art. Everyone has different ideas about what is beautiful and this story pours through the gamut."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433267</url></doc>
